fields.name: name_of_filter_sample
fields.title: Name of filter sample
fields.description: Name of filter sample

fields.name: volume_of_sampled_air(m^3)
fields.title: Volume of sampled air
fields.description: Volume of air sampled through respective filter between start and end of sampling. [cubic meter]

fields.name: volume_of_water_for_solution(m^3)
fields.title: Volume of water solution
fields.description: Volume of ultra-pure water (milliQ) used to wash sampled material off respective filter. [cubic meter]

fields.name: volume_of_droplet_for_freezing(m^3)
fields.title: Volume of droplet for freezing
fields.description: Volume of a droplet from the washing-off solution that is put into one of 96 compartments of a PCR tray as part of the measurement setup. [cubic meter]
